root: ^Congratulations ! You killed the monster I was hunting. I saw you fight, it was impressive!
^Sorry, I haven't introduced myself, my name is Sir Edward.
^By the way, what are you doing here ?
^"Name" ? I have never heard of you. Are you new around here ?
^You may be the chosen one the village has been waiting for. I need to know for sure. Follow me ! I will take you to the village chief.
